| **Typography** | Clean, traditional fonts | Readability, professionalism |
| **Headline** | "Grow Your Business with Confidence" | Benefit-focused, risk mitigation |
| **CTA** | "Start Free Trial" | Low-commitment, familiar action |
| **Social Proof** | "Trusted by 10,000+ companies" | Authority, established credibility |

### Version B: Bold & Disruption-Focused

| **Element** | **Implementation** | **Psychology** |
|-------------|-------------------|----------------|
| **Color Scheme** | Neon gradients (#00ff88, #ff0088, #0088ff) | Innovation, energy, disruption |
| **Typography** | Bold, impactful fonts | Urgency, confidence |
| **Headline** | "Dominate Your Market" | Action-oriented, competitive advantage |
| **CTA** | "Claim Your Edge â†’" | Urgency, exclusivity, forward momentum |
| **Social Proof** | "10x faster growth" | Aspirational, transformation |

